price: Sila Inni uumee (iccitii isaanii) hin beekuu! inni keessa argaafi beekaadha.
arabic: أَلَا يَعۡلَمُ مَنۡ خَلَقَ وَهُوَ ٱللَّطِيفُ ٱلۡخَبِيرُ

version.title: Oromo translation
version.description: Translation of the Quran meanings into Oromo by Ghaly Ababour Abaghuna, printed in 2009.

meta.transliteration: alā yaʿlamu man khalaqa wahuwa al-laṭīfu al-khabīru
